Text: Autowebcom Customer Satisfaction SurveyAutowebcom Customer Satisfaction Survey TO Kevin Hyatt EMAIL CUSTOMER FROM utowebcom SUBJECT Autowebcom Customer Satisfaction Survey Dear Kevin Your satisfaction is important to us so weve developed a survey to evaluate and improve our program By answering our Customer Satisfaction Survey you will help us improve the Autowebcom online shopping experience Click here to begin the survey surveyindexcfmprnum Your confirmation number is This request was for a Dodge Ram and was sent to Hazlewoods Dodge Country Some webbased email readers will not properly load this page if you click on the above link If you experience errors please copy the link and paste it into your browsers address bar Thank you for using Autowebcom Sincerely Jeffrey Schwartz President Chief Executive Officer Autowebcom
